      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained linguine </strong>and <strong>half</strong> the<strong> grated Italian hard cheese </strong>to the pan with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the pasta is fully coated in sauce – these are your <strong>beef meatballs with creamy linguine</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of the reserved starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
